<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Event Reminder</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
    <h2>Hello {{name}},</h2>
    <p>This is a friendly reminder that the event <strong>{{eventTitle}}</strong> you have tickets for is happening tomorrow!</p>
    <p><strong>Event Details:</strong></p>
    <ul>
        <li>Date & Time: {{eventDate}}</li>
        <li>Location: {{location}}</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We look forward to seeing you there. Don't forget to bring your tickets!</p>
    <br>
    <p>Best regards,</p>
    <p><strong>Ticketing Team</strong></p>
</body>
</html>
